  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Tegaserod (HTF919) is an aminoguanidine indole compound and a member of a new class of
      subgroup-selective 5-hydroxytryptamine (5-HT) agonists. The aim of this study is to
      investigate the efficacy, safety and tolerability of tegaserod on bowel habits in patients
      with CC.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
